==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: earned
<hw>earned</hw> <pr>(⟦etil⟧rnd)</pr>, <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Gained as a result of effort or action; -- used especially of
income; <as>as, <ex>earned</ex> income</as>. Contrasted with
<ant>unearned</ant>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Baseball)</fld> <def>not resulting from an error by
an opposing team; -- used in the phrase <ex>earned</ex> runs.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>earner</ent>⟦br⟧
